BIlHUvmk529JjmBkMk60apVqgvRsk-kyv9h_4B4aOXSQ" rel=3D"" style=3D"color: #1a1=
a1a; text-decoration: underline;">looking like a toy</a>, and you build for=
 the underserved, not just for moral reasons, but for strategic ones. It&#8=
217;s <strong>disruptive innovation</strong> meets the <strong>compounding =
power of young users</strong>. It&#8217;s more Roblox than Github. As Repli=
t&#8217;s CEO and co-founder <a href=3D"https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJ=
xFUMluhDAM_ZrJEWUBJjnk0Et_I8piIBpIUGI65e8bhkMly5ZlPb_FW4Q5l1PvuSK5msFzB53gX=
