acebook works, you get hired by the company, and then interview with teams =
inside of the company. And the internet.org team didn&#8217;t have room for=
 Amjad.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: =
26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">But at the same time, a small team at Facebook wa=
s working on building a new open source framework that would make it easier=
