=2E Amjad joined that team as a founding=20=
engineer, and spent nearly three yea=
rs building it out.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; l=
ine-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">The beauty of React Native is that it=
 lets developers write code in React, a best-in-class JavaScript library, t=
hat automatically works across platforms. That means that small companies m=
ight not need an iOS team and an Android team and teams for the long-tail o=
f platforms. One mobile team shares the same codebase, and React renders th=
e code to the native platform&#8217;s UI. One entrepreneur I spoke to this =
week brought up React Native unprompted, saying, &#8220;With tools like AWS=
, React Native, and more, we can do an enormous amount with a team of 10 pe=
ople.&#8221;&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-hei=
ght: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">All the while, while Amjad was working towar=
